Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:50.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I played against him in the Wakajishisen last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He scared me during the game with a few good moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:58.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but he was bad at Yose and I\Nwon by six and a half moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:04.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But, Touya persistently asked me about how he played.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:09.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was pissed off back then because he\Nkept asking about the guy who lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But I guess Touya really did think of him as a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:34.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Only I can measure Shindou's strength now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:41.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I knew the moment he appeared\Nin front of me that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I just need to wait..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:53.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,They've already prepared a match between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:59.99,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(350,115)}The Seventy-Second Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:59.99,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx330\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}And so they began to run
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:32.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It may look like he's foiling Shindou-kun's\Nattack on White in the center,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:37.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but Shindou-kun's planned for this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Murakami-san thought he was\Nfoiling Shindou-kun's advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:58.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but instead he wasted many moves,\Nand let Shindou-kun gain territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's lost all will to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He is Touya-kun's rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.01,Background,,0,0,0,,Have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.55,Background,,0,0,0,,So you will be coming to your\Nmatches from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will! I will! I won't be absent anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The pairings for the first preliminaries of the Meijin\Ntitle match should have been sent out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I got it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your opponent for the first round\Nwas Touya 3-dan, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun has a full match schedule, so\NI don't know when your match will be,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but good luck. There are some people\Nwho expect great things from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sorry. Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's expecting great things from Shindou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.75,Background,,0,0,0,,Amano-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Master Kuwabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He speaks of him as if he's Touya Akira's equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,'Oh'? You knew about it, Amano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.26,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun looks like nothing more\Nthan just another impolite kid to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.18,Background,,0,0,0,,just like any other kid these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd be happy if many more kids\Nlike Touya-kun, with real skill, appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The pro exam starts this week...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who will pass this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope whoever passes doesn't ditch\Ntheir matches like Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:47.07,Background,,0,0,0,,Amano-san, should we be hopeful\Nabout the future of the Go world?
